      • createBenchmarkFiles

        public void createBenchmarkFiles​(Configuration conf,
                                 Collection<LPProblem> problems,
                                 String name,
                                 String format)
        Creates the train, test and gold standard (test) files for the benchmark configuration and the problems Depending on the format will save these in json or turtle format to name-train.ttl name-test.ttl name-test-goldstd.ttl If Open World Assumption is used it will also validate the problems using an Openllet Reasoner.
        Parameters:
        conf - the benchmark configuration
        problems - the problems the abox should be created for
        name - the benchmark name
        format - json or turtle - will determine the output format
